    Class Description
    Aplication
    Main class responsible for initiating and running the application.
    ConnectionDB
    This interface manages the database connection by providing a method to establish a connection.
    DatabaseInitializer
    Utility class for initializing the system's database.
    DataFormatter
    Utility class for formatting data.
    PropertiesFileGenerator
    Utility class for generating Properties objects from a properties file.
    Researcher
    Represents a Researcher entity with various attributes.
    ResearcherController
    Controller class responsible for managing researcher-related operations between the user interface, service layer, and data model.
    ResearcherDao<Researcher,​Long>
    This interface defines the contract for Researcher Data Access Object (DAO) operations.
    ResearcherDTO
    Implementation of ResearcherDao interface responsible for database operations related to Researcher entities.
    ResearcherService
    Service class responsible for handling operations related to Researcher entities.
    SerpApiService
    Service class responsible for interacting with the SerpApi to fetch top researchers' data.
    UserInterface
    Represents the User Interface of the application.
